---
title: Moroccan-Style Turkey & Chickpea Stew with Pearl Couscous & Cilantro
description: This quick 20-minute meal of cinnamon- and cumin-seasoned beef packed with tender chickpeas and caramelized tomato paste was inspired by the cuisine of North Africa. Serve this satisfying stew over springy, nutty pearl couscous, and finish with a sprinkle of cilantro just before serving for pops of color and herbaceous flavor.
